OL,3,CTop doctor raising awareness of
OL,4,C'gentle' caesareans to improve
OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,FA leading birth doctor is calling for
OL,8,Fmore awareness of 'gentle' caesareans
OL,9,Fto help improve the experience of
OL,10,Fpeople giving birth in Wales.
OL,12,FGentle caesareans - sometimes referred
OL,13,Fto as 'natural' or 'family-centred'
OL,14,Fcaesareans - aim to prioritise
OL,15,Fimmediate skin-to-skin contact and
OL,16,Fdelayed cord clamping.
OL,18,FFamilies are also allowed to have the
OL,19,Fscreen down in order to see the baby
OL,20,Femerging from the womb, play their own
OL,21,Fmusic and take photos of the birth.
