OL,7,FHywel Dda University Health Board's
OL,8,Flead consultant for obstetrician and
OL,9,Fgynaecology hopes to see his approach
OL,10,Fbecome the norm and a move away from
OL,11,Fthe term 'gentle'.
OL,13,FIhab Abbasi first came across the
OL,14,Fconcept when he was a trainee in
OL,15,FEngland but initially felt sceptical.
