OL,3,CTop doctor raising awareness of
OL,4,C'gentle' caesareans to improve
OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,F"I remember a woman coming in asking
OL,8,Ffor the light to be dimmed, music to
OL,9,Fbe played, to have the baby skin-to-
OL,10,Fskin straight away, for us not to rush
OL,11,Fand cut the cord straight away," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"I remember the team was thinking 'no
OL,15,Fthis is just ridiculous, we're not
OL,16,Fgoing to do that, we're just going to
OL,17,Fdo what we want to do'."
