OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,FA few years later his now wife, a
OL,8,Fcounsellor who often deals with birth
OL,9,Ftrauma, asked him whether he had tried
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,FIn 2018, he carried out his first
OL,13,Fgentle caesarean and said he has never
OL,14,Flooked back.
OL,16,F"I went into the theatre thinking this
OL,17,Fis the most ridiculous thing, it's
OL,18,Fjust for show, and I came out thinking
OL,19,Fthis is the only way I'm going to do a
OL,20,Fcaesarean.
