OL,7,F"The actual surgical technique doesn't
OL,8,Fdiffer a lot - you're going to have to
OL,9,Fmake the cut the same way and close
OL,10,Fthe layers the same way - it's the
OL,11,Fbirth itself."
OL,13,FMr Abbasi said mothers have previously
OL,14,Ftold him their experience was "rushed,
OL,15,Ftheir baby was taken away from (them),
OL,16,Fand the baby was wrapped when they
OL,17,Fcame to (them)".
