OL,7,FFamilies at Glangwili Hospital are
OL,8,Fencouraged to take photos and videos
OL,9,Fof the birth and bring their own music
OL,10,Fwhich can be played out through
OL,11,Fspeakers in the theatre.
OL,13,FThe anaesthetist attaches monitors to
OL,14,Fthe mother's back, rather than across
OL,15,Fthe chest, so that she can have
OL,16,Fimmediate skin contact with the baby
OL,17,Fwithout wires getting in the way.
