OL,7,FOnce Mr Abbasi helps the baby's head
OL,8,Femerge he encourages mothers to push,
OL,9,Fwhich he said helps them "feel part of
OL,10,Fit".
OL,12,FMothers can also choose whether they
OL,13,Fwould like the screen down in order to
OL,14,Fsee their baby being born.
