OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,F"Therefore why would we need to pass
OL,8,Fit to a midwife who's going to take
OL,9,Fthem, why wouldn't the mum be the
OL,10,Ffirst one to cwtch her baby?"
OL,12,FVictoria Thomas and Robert Thomas had
OL,13,Ftheir third caesarean birth earlier
OL,14,Fthis month and described the
OL,15,Fexperience at Glangwili Hospital as
OL,16,F"magical".
