OL,7,FSpeaking after the birth, Victoria
OL,8,Fsaid: "I had no experience before of
OL,9,Fpushing the baby out, to be able to do
OL,10,Fthat and be involved in that was
OL,11,Freally magical."
OL,13,FRobert added: "It felt a lot calmer.
OL,14,FIt wasn't as rushed and it was much
OL,15,Fmore personal."
