OL,7,FMr Abbasi and his team collected data
OL,8,Fto investigate any potential safety
OL,9,Fconcerns and found there was no
OL,10,Fincreased risk of infection, less
OL,11,Fbleeding and improved outcomes for
OL,12,Fbabies.
OL,14,FTheatre practitioner Catrin Sykes,
OL,15,Fresponsible for keeping the theatre
OL,16,Fsterile, said patient safety remains
OL,17,Fthe priority.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/19
