OL,3,CTop doctor raising awareness of
OL,4,C'gentle' caesareans to improve
OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,F"We make sure that the risk of
OL,8,Finfection is still less, the patient
OL,9,Fwill always be our priority. We would
OL,10,Fnever do anything to put patients at
OL,11,Fharm," she said.
OL,13,F"We keep them informed and just let
OL,14,Fthem know what's going on at all times.
OL,16,F"Everyone in the theatre's got their
OL,17,Fown roles and skills and we're all
OL,18,Fmixed together to make sure everything
OL,19,Fis as safe as possible for the
OL,20,Fpatient."
