OL,7,FClinical and operational lead midwife
OL,8,FAlison Jones said there has also been
OL,9,F"significant" changes in the use of
OL,10,Flanguage.
OL,12,F"A very significant change that I have
OL,13,Fseen is instead of us being involved
OL,14,Fin the 'delivery' of a baby, we are
OL,15,Fthere to support the birth of a baby.
OL,16,FIt's very much the mum and the family
OL,17,Fand that baby at the centre of what we
OL,18,Fdo," she said.
