OL,3,CTop doctor raising awareness of
OL,4,C'gentle' caesareans to improve
OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,F"Having babies is very natural but it
OL,8,Falso comes with a lot of fear and a
OL,9,Flot of unknown. It's not an exact
OL,10,Fscience having babies and there's no
OL,11,Finstruction book that comes along with
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,F"As a midwifery profession we're
OL,15,Fcentral in supporting the mums and
OL,16,Ffamilies in growing their confidence
OL,17,Fand supporting them to be at the
OL,18,Fcentre - what they choose is what we
OL,19,Fwill support."
