OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,FMr Abbasi believes a lack of awareness
OL,8,Fand resistance to change are the main
OL,9,Freasons why gentle caesareans are not
OL,10,Fyet the norm.
OL,12,FHe and the team want to see the term
OL,13,F'gentle' eradicated.
OL,15,F"I don't want to give it a different
OL,16,Fname. I want to have the day that
OL,17,Fevery caesarean is focused on the mum
OL,18,Fand making sure it's a birth
OL,19,Fexperience," he said.
