OL,7,F"I feel more awareness of this makes
OL,8,Fmore women want to ask for it and then
OL,9,Fthat will force the doctors to start
OL,10,Frethinking the way they're doing it."
OL,12,FJust over a third of babies in Wales
OL,13,Fwere born by caesarean in 2022, the
OL,14,Fhighest percentage on record,
OL,15,Faccording to the most up-to-date
OL,16,Ffigures from Stats Wales.
