OL,3,CTop doctor raising awareness of
OL,4,C'gentle' caesareans to improve
OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,FClinical guidelines issued by NHS
OL,8,FScotland in 2022 set out four core
OL,9,Fprinciples to gentle caesareans: the
OL,10,Fpromotion of a holistic birth
OL,11,Fexperience, slow delivery of the baby
OL,12,Fwithout fundal pressure, optimal cord
OL,13,Fclamping and early skin-to-skin
OL,14,Fcontact.
OL,16,FStudies have shown that this
OL,17,Fadaptation of the traditional
OL,18,Fcaesarean does not cause any increased
OL,19,Frisk of complications for mothers or
OL,20,Fbabies.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/19
