OL,3,CTop doctor raising awareness of
OL,4,C'gentle' caesareans to improve
OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,FIt is hoped that by allowing a slow
OL,8,Fdelivery of the baby without the use
OL,9,Fof fundal pressure - which involves
OL,10,Fsomeone pushing on the uterus to
OL,11,Fassist the birth - a more
OL,12,Fphysiological birth is achieved as
OL,13,Fwell as enhancing the birth experience
OL,14,Ffor the woman or birthing person and
OL,15,Ftheir partner.
OL,17,FEarly skin-to-skin contact is
OL,18,Fassociated with improved bonding,
OL,19,Finfant feeding, breastfeeding outcomes
OL,20,Fand infant crying.
