OL,4,C'gentle' caesareans to improve
OL,5,Cchildbirth
OL,7,FThe Scottish guidance is for gentle
OL,8,Fcaesareans to be offered and discussed
OL,9,Fin the antenatal clinic at the booking
OL,10,Fappointment for anyone considering a
OL,11,Fcaesarean birth.
OL,13,FWhile there are no such guidelines in
OL,14,FWales, the Welsh Government has
OL,15,Fwelcomed the work being done in west
OL,16,FWales, adding that it expects a
OL,17,F"family-centred approach" during all
OL,18,Fpregnancies and births.
